# Local/generated ASQA material. Keep the small fixed splits and manifests.
data/asqa/corpus/
data/asqa/normalized/
data/asqa/raw/
data/asqa/downloads/
!data/asqa/splits/
!data/asqa/splits/**
!data/asqa/manifests/
